# Library API

This project is a simple Express server application for managing 
a library with users, posts, and comments. 
It includes middleware for logging requests and 
handling errors, and it uses EJS as the view engine.

## Project Structure

```plaintext
.
├── middleware
│   ├── authMiddleware.js
│   ├── errorMiddleware.js
│   └── logMiddleware.js
├── models
│   ├── comments.js
│   ├── posts.js
│   └── users.js
├── public
│   └── css
│       └── styles.css
├── routes
│   ├── comments.js
│   ├── posts
